                    <li>
                        <h4>Web Development:</h4>
                        <p>Languages: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, Ruby on Rails</p>
                        <p>Frameworks: React.js, Angular.js (JavaScript), Laravel (PHP), Ruby on Rails (Ruby)</p>
